}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "MADE IN CHINA" and "PU20114-3G0B" is silkscreened on the board. :The '''NEC''' hub controller IC package is marked with "NEC", "720114", and "125E4". :The manufacturer (seems to be a [http://www.sunrichtech.com.hk/assign.asp?keyid=ba3 '''Sunrich Technology''' U-271...]) is almost certainly the same as the [[Rosewill RHUB-300]].
The model on the device's label is '''USB 2.0 4PB'''.
The power adapter included with the device is an '''unbranded''' ''JD-050-020'' (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz -> 5VDC 2.0A).
